name: Aratech Corporation (V)
Lore: 'Aratech Corporation sent support staff to various Imperial outposts and garrisons. Gave advanced briefings and training to biker scout personnel.',
Text: 'Deploy on table.  AT-STs and speeder bikes are power and forfeit +1.  During your deploy phase, may reveal an AT-ST or Speeder Bike from hand to take a unique (•) [Endor] Imperial pilot of ability < 3 (or vice versa) into hand from Reserve Deck, and deploy both simultaneously; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
